{"tid":1510174,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有網站懸紅緝捕示威者，網站登記人為梁振英。","createTime":"2019-08-27T05:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T06:45:10.000Z","uid":125349,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b4d8715cf9c22c6e453580611380891892a029b8","tid":1510174,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:43:30.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】有人呼籲市民就反修例運動期間的示威活動提供資料，懸紅緝拿相關疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n名為「803行動」的網頁呼籲市民就至今30宗暴力事件提供資料，其中塗污中聯辦外的國徽事件提供懸紅100萬元；而立法會被衝擊當晚有人噴黑立法會區徽，則懸紅50萬元，懸紅賞金全部來自民間，日後亦會眾籌。經翻查網頁域名，這網站的登記日期是本月12日，而持有人名稱為梁振英。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=360621&amp;fbclid=IwAR1bUWiPcsiqMbbRuPQLK0yHJteLo16klnopi_abH0L4LPRMlOZ_zOVzElc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360621%26fbclid%3DIwAR1bUWiPcsiqMbbRuPQLK0yHJteLo16klnopi_abH0L4LPRMlOZ_zOVzElc&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=d1c5cf64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360621%26fbclid%3DIwAR1bUWiPcsiqMbbRuPQLK0yHJteLo16klnopi_abH0L4LPRMlOZ_zOVzElc&h=13d418b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=360621&amp;fbclid=IwAR1bUWiPcsiqMbbRuPQLK0yHJteLo16klnopi_abH0L4LPRMlOZ_zOVzElc</a>"},{"pid":"efc09f0564b40281d5453badbc240c367c34c914","tid":1510174,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=5ea3bfdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen